          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-1" n="1">I.<lb/><hi rend="display-initial">F</hi>L<hi rend="small-caps">UTT'RING</hi> spread thy purple Pinions,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-2" n="2">Gentle <hi rend="italics">Cupid</hi> o'er my Heart;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-3" n="3">I a Slave in thy Dominions;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-4" n="4">Nature must give Way to Art.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-5" n="5">II.<lb/>Mild <hi rend="italics">Arcadians</hi>, ever blooming,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-6" n="6">Nightly nodding o'er your Flocks;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-7" n="7">See my weary Days consuming,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-8" n="8">All beneath yon' flow'ry Rocks.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-9" n="9">III.<lb/>Thus, the <hi rend="italics">Cyprian</hi> Goddess weeping,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-10" n="10">Mourn'd <hi rend="italics">Adonis</hi>, darling Youth:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-11" n="11">Him the Boar in Silence creeping,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-12" n="12">Gor'd with unrelenting Tooth.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-13" n="13">IV.<lb/><hi rend="italics">Cynthia</hi>, tune harmonious Numbers;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-14" n="14">Fair Discretion string the Lyre;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-15" n="15">Sooth my ever-waking Slumbers:</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-16" n="16">Bright <hi rend="italics">Apollo</hi> lend thy Choir.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-17" n="17">V.<lb/>Gloomy <hi rend="italics">Pluto</hi>, King of Terrors,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-18" n="18">Arm'd in adamantine Chains,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-19" n="19">Lead me to the Chrystal Mirrors,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-20" n="20">Wat'ring soft <hi rend="italics">Elysian</hi> Plains.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-21" n="21">VI.<lb/>Mournful Cypress, verdant Willow,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-22" n="22">Gilding my <hi rend="italics">Aurelia</hi>'s Brows,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-23" n="23"><hi rend="italics">Morpheus</hi> hov'ring o'er my Pillow,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-24" n="24">Hear me pay my dying Vows.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-25" n="25">VII.<lb/>Melancholy smooth <hi rend="italics">Meander</hi>,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-26" n="26">Swiftly purling in a Round,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-27" n="27">On thy Margin Lovers wander,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-28" n="28">With thy flow'ry Chaplets crown'd.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-29" n="29">VIII.<lb/>Thus, when <hi rend="italics">Philomela</hi> drooping,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-30" n="30">Softly seeks her silent Mate;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-31" n="31">See the Bird of <hi rend="italics">Juno</hi> stooping,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-0203-line-32" n="32">Melody resigns to Fate.</l>
          </lg>
